rows.label: tlk006701_05_msg0001
rows.name:
There was an explosion over by the
World Tree! Were you all okay?

rows.label: tlk006701_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I've never been so glad to be
stationed here at the Torigo base...

rows.label: tlk006701_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I know the homeland is in an unprecedented
crisis, but a mere soldier like me
can't do anything to help...

rows.label: tlk006701_05_msg0004
rows.name:
The least I can do is properly
look after the people who have
evacuated to the Torigo base...

rows.label: tlk006701_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Meleph-sama!? Why are you
in a place like this?

rows.label: tlk006701_05_msg0006
rows.name:
Could it be that you were
worried about us stationed
in Gula!? What an honor!

rows.label: tlk006701_05_msg0007
rows.name:
If someone like Meleph-sama were my
direct superior, I'm sure my work
would be so much more rewarding...
